de.hsos.ecs.richwps.wpsmonitor.data.config

Class MonitorConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsos.ecs.richwps.wpsmonitor.data.config.MonitorConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public final class MonitorConfig
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable
    Representate the configuration of a Monitor instance. For this purpose, the MonitorConfig will be used a extended version of the Properties class. All configurations will be read out of a properties file. If the save-method is called, all changed properties will be written back into the properties file. If a config is not valid, then the default properties is used as fallback.
    Author:
    Florian Vogelpohl
